32
00:01:07.670 --> 00:01:09.875
the same functions as
a hardware firewall,

33
00:01:09.875 --> 00:01:11.884
but it's not a physical device.

34
00:01:11.884 --> 00:01:13.820
Instead, it's a software program

35
00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:16.340
installed on a computer
or on a server.

36
00:01:16.340 --> 00:01:18.980
If the software firewall is
installed on a computer,

37
00:01:18.980 --> 00:01:20.660
it will analyze all the traffic

38
00:01:20.660 --> 00:01:22.450
received by that computer.

39
00:01:22.450 --> 00:01:25.280
If the software firewall
is installed on a server,

40
00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:28.840
it will protect all the devices
connected to the server.

41
00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:31.490
A software firewall
typically costs

42
